{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be minimalist and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Design Co.</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            min-height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0056b3 0%, #007bff 100%);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n        #hero .container {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #0056b3;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        #services .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            flex-basis: calc(33.333% - 40px);\n            margin: 20px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #0056b3;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #e9ecef;\n        }\n        #contact .container {\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .contact-details {\n            flex-basis: 50%;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            flex-basis: 45%;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #003d80;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #343a40;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #007bff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 30px 15px;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .service-item {\n                flex-basis: 100%;\n            }\n            .contact-info {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .contact-details, .contact-form {\n                flex-basis: 100%;\n                margin-bottom: 30px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Aura Design Co.</h1>\n            <p>Crafting Digital Experiences</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Elevate Your Brand with Stunning Design</h2>\n            <p>We create captivating visuals and user-friendly interfaces that drive results.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Quote</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-paint-brush\"></i>\n                <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n                <p>Intuitive and engaging user interfaces for seamless experiences.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-code\"></i>\n                <h3>Web Development</h3>\n                <p>Modern, responsive websites that perform exceptionally.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-bullhorn\"></i>\n                <h3>Branding & Strategy</h3>\n                <p>Building strong brand identities that resonate with your audience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Aura Design Co. is a collective of passionate designers and developers dedicated to bringing your vision to life. We believe in clean aesthetics, functional design, and collaborative partnerships.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Let's Create Something Amazing</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <div class=\"contact-details\">\n                    <p>Email: info@auradesign.co</p>\n                    <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n                    <p>Follow us: <a href=\"#\">LinkedIn</a> | <a href=\"#\">Dribbble</a></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                    <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                        <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                        <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                        <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n                        <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                    </form>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Design Co. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}